description: Phased development comprising (a) demolition of existing building and (b) construction of a building up to 17 storeys comprising flexible employment space (Class E(g)) on part-ground floor and part first floor and purpose-built student accommodation (Sui Generis) on part ground and upper floors with ancillary plant, refuse and laundry facilities (Class E(g) and Sui Generis) at lower ground floor, and associated cycle parking, new public realm, and landscaping.
